  "types": [
    {
      "name": "KarmaAccount",
      "docs": [
        "Public, append-only karma counters for a TID. Lives at PDA",
        "`[\"karma\", tid_le_bytes]`. Anyone can fund the account into",
        "existence; only the per-source `record_*` instructions can",
        "increment the counters, and each source record (a tip, a task)",
        "can only be counted once thanks to the KarmaProof PDA."
      ],
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "tid",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "tips_received_count",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "tips_received_lamports",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "tasks_completed_count",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "tasks_completed_reward_lamports",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "bump",
            "type": "u8"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "KarmaAccountInitialized",
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "karma",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "tid",
            "type": "u64"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "KarmaProof",
      "docs": [
        "One per (source record, karma account) pair. Lives at PDA",
        "`[\"karma-proof\", source_record_pubkey]`. Existence is the only",
        "signal we read — `init` on the account guarantees that the same",
        "source record can't be credited twice."
      ],
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "source",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "kind",
            "docs": [
              "1 = tip-registry::TipRecord, 2 = task-registry::Task."
            ],
            "type": "u8"
          },
          {
            "name": "tid",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "bump",
            "type": "u8"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Task",
      "docs": [
        "One per task. Lives at PDA",
        "`[\"task\", creator_pubkey, task_id_le]`. Like Crowdfund, this PDA",
        "doubles as the reward escrow vault — when `reward_amount > 0` the",
        "creator transfers that many lamports into the PDA on creation,",
        "and complete/cancel mutate them out via direct lamport mutation."
      ],
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "creator",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "creator_tid",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "task_id",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "status",
            "type": "u8"
          },
          {
            "name": "reward_amount",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "claimer",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "claimer_tid",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "has_claimer",
            "type": "bool"
          },
          {
            "name": "created_at",
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "claimed_at",
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "completed_at",
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "metadata_hash",
            "type": {
              "array": [
                "u8",
                32
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "bump",
            "type": "u8"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "TaskKarmaRecorded",
